orPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"toile","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Le Salon Louis XIII a conserv\u00e9 la quasi-totalit\u00e9 du d\u00e9cor mis en place \u00e0 la fin du r\u00e8gne d\u0027Henri IV. Les quinze toiles de Dubois (Inv. 4144, Inv. 4158, Inv. 4145, Inv. 4147, Inv. 4146, Inv. 4148, Inv. 4149, Inv. 4150, Inv. 4151, F1980-2, Inv. 4152, Inv. 4153, Inv. 4154, Inv. 4155, Inv. 4156) racontant l\u0027Histoire de Th\u00e9ag\u00e8ne et Charicl\u00e9e, amants contrari\u00e9s dont l\u0027histoire f\u00eet l\u0027objet d\u0027un roman grec du IV si\u00e8cle \u00e9crit par H\u00e9liodore d\u0027Em\u00e8se et traduit au XVI\u00e8me si\u00e8cle par Amyot, furent install\u00e9es aussi bien aux murs qu\u0027au plafond entre les poutres ma\u00eetresses. La premi\u00e8re mention connue du d\u00e9cor remonte \u00e0 1609. \r\nSous le r\u00e8gne de Louis XV, quatre tableaux et d\u0027autres compositions furent d\u00e9croch\u00e9es pour faciliter des travaux. \r\nEn 1794, des quatre tableaux d\u00e9croch\u00e9s il ne reste plus que trois. Ils furent probablement achemin\u00e9s au Louvre, puis install\u00e9es en 1837 dans la pi\u00e8ce adjacente au salon Louis XIII, o\u00f9 on peut encore les voir aujourd\u0027hui. \r\nUn des tableaux, \u00bb Charicl\u00e9e enlev\u00e9e par Trachin \u00bb (Acquis en 1980 par le Ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau, F 1980-2), dispar\u00fbt des collections jusqu\u0027\u00e0 l\u0027ann\u00e9e 1980, date \u00e0 laquelle il r\u00e9appara\u00eet sur le march\u00e9 de l\u0027art. \r\nIl est acquis alors par le ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau.\r\nLa s\u00e9rie fut port\u00e9e \u00e0 Zuccaro sur l\u0027Inventaire de 1832.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"entr\u00e9e - Collection de Henri IV","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Peintures","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e national du ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau, Fontainebleau","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"entr\u00e9e - Collection de Henri IV"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057518","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057519","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057520","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057521","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057522","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057523","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057524","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057525","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057526","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057527","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057528","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010057529","type":"El\u00e9ment d\u0027un ensemble"}],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000057517\/0000920157_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000057517\/0000920157_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2018 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Thierry Ollivier","type":"face, recto, avers, avan